      <title>Europol leads international operation against environmental crime and waste trafficking</title>
      <link>https://www.europol.europa.eu/media-press/newsroom/news/europol-leads-international-operation-against-environmental-crime-and-waste-trafficking</link>
      <description>Europol has successfully coordinated a large-scale operation targeting organised crime networks involved in waste and pollution crime. The global operation, code-named ‘Custos Viridis’, took place between January and December 2025 on five continents, with Europol working alongside partners from 71 countries and numerous international organisations.</description>
